Blacknightmare::

Blacknightmare walked to Shuttle and she sat down, Shuttle took off 
and left BlackFortress. Beliving that Orchestra was still in 
BLackFortress, Blacknightmare took a decition and sent a secret 
message to Orchestra. 

"Orchestra" said the message "I have to go a mission and I guess when 
I come back you'll have gone to do yours. I just liked to say goodbye 
and good luck. I'll be back. Take care, Orchestra. Blacknightmare"

She sent the message, and shuttle moved towards Infectron's second 
base.
